[6.104, "o", "\u001b[4A\n\u001b[1;38;5;42m\u2714\u001b[0m on the mesh as \"demo-laptop\" (fd53:74d4:1681::1) \u2014 no ports opened\u001b[K\r\n\u001b[1;38;5;42m\u2714\u001b[0m found a local model \u00b7 ollama-native (llama3.2:3b)\u001b[K\r\n\u001b[38;5;39m\u28ef \u001b[0m \u001b[38;5;241mPublishing it as a private service\u2026\u001b[0m\u001b[K\r\n\r"]
